  (text "POWER MANAGEMENT\n\nBuck Converter (LMR51430):\n- Input: DC_BUS (up to 36V from aux tap)\n- Output: +15V @ 1A\n- Switching: 2.1MHz\n- Sync buck topology\n\nLDO (XC6220):\n- Input: +15V (could also be 5V)\n- Output: +3.3V @ 700mA\n- Low noise: 6.5µV RMS\n\nReference:\n- LMR51430_THERMAL_ANALYSIS.md\n- BOM.md Section 2"
