  (text "BUCK CONVERTER DESIGN NOTES:\n\nVout = 1.0V × (1 + R_FB1/R_FB2)\n     = 1.0V × (1 + 100k/7.15k)\n     = 15.0V\n\nfsw = 2.1MHz (fixed)\nL = 6.8µH (SRP1038A)\nCout = 44µF (2×22µF)\nCin = 2.2µF 100V\n\nThermal: Rθja = 45°C/W (SOT-23-6)\nMax Pdiss at 85°C = 0.89W"
    (exclude_from_sim no)
    (at 25.4 170.18 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27)) (justify left))
    (uuid "text-design-notes-001")
  )

  (text "LDO DESIGN NOTES:\n\nXC6220B331MR-G\n- Fixed 3.3V output\n- 700mA max\n- 6.5µVrms noise\n- Dropout: 100mV @ 200mA\n\nCin = 10µF (low ESR)\nCout = 22µF (low ESR)\n\nPdiss = (Vin - Vout) × Iout\n      = (15V - 3.3V) × 0.3A\n      = 3.5W (needs heatsinking!)\n\nNote: Consider 5V intermediate\nrail to reduce LDO dissipation"
    (exclude_from_sim no)
    (at 25.4 200.66 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27)) (justify left))
    (uuid "text-ldo-notes-001")
  )

)
